        <h1 class="page-title">Link</h1>
        <p class="page-desc">
          TextLink is an interactive inline or standalone text-based navigation component. It supports multiple visual styles, three layout types, configurable underline behavior, and full RTL support.
        </p>
        <nav class="content-tabs">
          <button class="tab-item active">Overview</button>
