      <!-- ======= CODE TAB ======= -->
      <div class="tab-content" id="tab-code" style="display: none; padding-top: 32px;">
        <h2 id="live-demo-code" class="doc-section-title">Live demo (Code)</h2>
        <p class="doc-section-subtitle">Configure the Link and view the generated HTML.</p>

        <style>
          .link-playground { border: 1px solid var(--prism-border); border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; background: var(--prism-surface); margin-bottom: 48px; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); }
          [data-theme="light"] .link-playground { background: #fff; border: 1px solid rgba(37,99,235,0.1); box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(37,99,235,0.08); }
          .link-pg-toolbar { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 20px; padding: 16px 24px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--prism-border); background: var(--prism-surface-hover); }
          [data-theme="light"] .link-pg-toolbar { background: rgba(248, 250, 255, 0.6); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(37,99,235,0.1); }
          .link-pg-group { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; flex: 1; min-width: 140px; }
          .link-pg-label { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--prism-text-muted); }
          .link-pg-select, .link-pg-input { background: var(--prism-surface); border: 1px solid var(--prism-border); color: var(--prism-text); padding: 8px 12px; border-radius: 8px; outline: none; font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.2s; }
          [data-theme="light"] .link-pg-select, [data-theme="light"] .link-pg-input { background: #fff; border-color: rgba(37,99,235,0.15); color: #1e293b; }
          .link-pg-select:focus, .link-pg-input:focus { border-color: var(--prism-violet); box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(37,99,235,0.15); }
          .link-pg-preview { padding: 60px; min-height: 180px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; background: #0a0a0c; background-image: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 20px 20px; }
          [data-theme="light"] .link-pg-preview { background: #ffffff; background-image: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(37,99,235,0.08) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 20px 20px; }
          .link-pg-code-header { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 12px 24px; background: var(--prism-surface); border-top: 1px solid var(--prism-border); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--prism-border); }
          [data-theme="light"] .link-pg-code-header { background: rgba(248, 250, 255, 0.8); border-color: rgba(37,99,235,0.1); }
          .link-pg-copy { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; background: transparent; border: none; font-family: inherit; font-size: 13.5px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--prism-text-muted); cursor: pointer; padding: 6px 12px; border-radius: 6px; transition: all 0.2s; }
          .link-pg-copy:hover { background: var(--prism-surface-hover); color: var(--prism-text); }
          [data-theme="light"] .link-pg-copy:hover { background: rgba(37,99,235,0.08); color: var(--prism-violet); }
          .link-pg-code { background: #0a0a0c; padding: 24px; overflow-x: auto; font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; color: #e2e8f0; margin: 0; white-space: pre; }
          .link-pg-code .tk-tag { color: #a78bfa; }
          .link-pg-code .tk-attr { color: #38bdf8; }
          .link-pg-code .tk-str { color: #34d399; }
          .link-pg-code .tk-punct { color: #94a3b8; }
        </style>

        <div class="link-playground">
          <div class="link-pg-toolbar">
            <div class="link-pg-group">
              <label class="link-pg-label">Style</label>
              <select class="link-pg-select" id="link-pg-style">
                <option value="primary" selected>Primary</option>
                <option value="secondary">Secondary</option>
                <option value="subtle">Subtle</option>
                <option value="danger">Danger</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            <div class="link-pg-group">
              <label class="link-pg-label">Size</label>
              <select class="link-pg-select" id="link-pg-size">
                <option value="sm">Small</option>
                <option value="md" selected>Medium</option>
                <option value="lg">Large</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            <div class="link-pg-group">
              <label class="link-pg-label">Underline</label>
              <select class="link-pg-select" id="link-pg-underline">
                <option value="always" selected>Always</option>
                <option value="hover">Hover only</option>
                <option value="none">None</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            <div class="link-pg-group">
              <label class="link-pg-label">Icon</label>
              <select class="link-pg-select" id="link-pg-icon">
                <option value="none" selected>None</option>
                <option value="leading">Leading</option>
                <option value="trailing">Trailing</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            <div class="link-pg-group">
              <label class="link-pg-label">Label</label>
              <input class="link-pg-input" id="link-pg-text" type="text" value="Read more">
            </div>
            <div class="link-pg-group">
              <label class="link-pg-label">href</label>
              <input class="link-pg-input" id="link-pg-href" type="text" value="#">
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="link-pg-preview">
            <a href="#" class="link-demo link-primary link-md link-underline-always" id="link-pg-preview" onclick="return false;">Read more</a>
          </div>

          <div class="link-pg-code-header">
            <div style="font-size: 13.5px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--prism-text);">HTML</div>
            <button class="link-pg-copy" id="link-pg-copy-btn">
              <svg width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8 7v8a2 2 0 002 2h6M8 7V5a2 2 0 012-2h4.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l4.414 4.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V15a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2M8 7H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h8a2 2 0 002-2v-2"/></svg>
              Copy code
            </button>
          </div>
          <pre class="link-pg-code" id="link-pg-code"></pre>
        </div>

        <script>
          (function(){
            const el = {
              style: document.getElementById('link-pg-style'),
              size: document.getElementById('link-pg-size'),
              underline: document.getElementById('link-pg-underline'),
              icon: document.getElementById('link-pg-icon'),
              text: document.getElementById('link-pg-text'),
              href: document.getElementById('link-pg-href'),
              preview: document.getElementById('link-pg-preview'),
              code: document.getElementById('link-pg-code'),
              copy: document.getElementById('link-pg-copy-btn')
            };
            if (!el.preview) return;

            const ARROW_SVG = '<svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>';

            function escape(s){ return s.replace(/</g,'&lt;').replace(/>/g,'&gt;').replace(/"/g,'&quot;'); }

            function render(){
              const style = el.style.value;
              const size = el.size.value;
              const underline = el.underline.value;
              const icon = el.icon.value;
              const label = el.text.value || 'Link';
              const href = el.href.value || '#';
              const classes = ['link-demo', 'link-' + style, 'link-' + size, 'link-underline-' + underline];

              let inner = '';
              if (icon === 'leading') inner += ARROW_SVG + '<span>' + escape(label) + '</span>';
              else if (icon === 'trailing') inner += '<span>' + escape(label) + '</span>' + ARROW_SVG;
              else inner += escape(label);

              el.preview.className = classes.join(' ');
              el.preview.setAttribute('href', href);
              el.preview.innerHTML = inner;

              const classAttr = classes.join(' ');
              let parts = [];
              const attrLine = '<span class="tk-punct">&lt;</span><span class="tk-tag">a</span> <span class="tk-attr">href</span><span class="tk-punct">=</span><span class="tk-str">"' + escape(href) + '"</span> <span class="tk-attr">class</span><span class="tk-punct">=</span><span class="tk-str">"' + classAttr + '"</span><span class="tk-punct">&gt;</span>';
              if (icon === 'leading') {
                parts.push(attrLine);
                parts.push('  <span class="tk-punct">&lt;</span><span class="tk-tag">svg</span> <span class="tk-attr">...</span><span class="tk-punct">&gt;&lt;/</span><span class="tk-tag">svg</span><span class="tk-punct">&gt;</span>');
                parts.push('  <span class="tk-punct">&lt;</span><span class="tk-tag">span</span><span class="tk-punct">&gt;</span>' + escape(label) + '<span class="tk-punct">&lt;/</span><span class="tk-tag">span</span><span class="tk-punct">&gt;</span>');
                parts.push('<span class="tk-punct">&lt;/</span><span class="tk-tag">a</span><span class="tk-punct">&gt;</span>');
              } else if (icon === 'trailing') {
                parts.push(attrLine);
                parts.push('  <span class="tk-punct">&lt;</span><span class="tk-tag">span</span><span class="tk-punct">&gt;</span>' + escape(label) + '<span class="tk-punct">&lt;/</span><span class="tk-tag">span</span><span class="tk-punct">&gt;</span>');
                parts.push('  <span class="tk-punct">&lt;</span><span class="tk-tag">svg</span> <span class="tk-attr">...</span><span class="tk-punct">&gt;&lt;/</span><span class="tk-tag">svg</span><span class="tk-punct">&gt;</span>');
                parts.push('<span class="tk-punct">&lt;/</span><span class="tk-tag">a</span><span class="tk-punct">&gt;</span>');
              } else {
                parts.push(attrLine + escape(label) + '<span class="tk-punct">&lt;/</span><span class="tk-tag">a</span><span class="tk-punct">&gt;</span>');
              }
              el.code.innerHTML = parts.join('\n');
            }
            ['style','size','underline','icon'].forEach(k => el[k].addEventListener('change', render));
            ['text','href'].forEach(k => el[k].addEventListener('input', render));
            el.copy.addEventListener('click', () => {
              navigator.clipboard.writeText(el.code.innerText).then(() => {
                const orig = el.copy.innerHTML;
                el.copy.innerHTML = '<svg width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> Copied';
                setTimeout(() => { el.copy.innerHTML = orig; }, 1800);
              });
            });
            render();
          })();
        </script>

        <hr class="doc-divider" />

        <h2 id="component-properties" class="doc-section-title">Component Properties</h2>
        <p class="doc-section-subtitle">Configurable properties exposed by the TextLink component.</p>

        <div class="doc-section">
          <table class="size-table">
            <thead><tr><th>Property</th><th>Type</th><th>Default</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr><td><code>Label</code></td><td>string</td><td>"Text Link"</td><td>The visible text content of the link.</td></tr>
              <tr><td><code>Show Leading Icon</code></td><td>boolean</td><td>false</td><td>Toggles the visibility of the leading icon slot.</td></tr>
              <tr><td><code>Show Trailing Icon</code></td><td>boolean</td><td>false</td><td>Toggles the visibility of the trailing icon slot.</td></tr>
              <tr><td><code>Leading Icon</code></td><td>ReactNode | SVGElement</td><td>undefined</td><td>Icon element placed before the label text.</td></tr>
              <tr><td><code>Trailing Icon</code></td><td>ReactNode | SVGElement</td><td>undefined</td><td>Icon element placed after the label text.</td></tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>

        <hr class="doc-divider" />

        <div class="doc-section">
          <h2 id="variant-axis-reference" class="doc-section-title">Variant Axis Reference</h2>
          <p class="doc-section-subtitle">Complete axis configuration for the TextLink component set.</p>
          <table class="size-table">
            <thead><tr><th>Axis</th><th>Values</th><th>Default</th></tr></thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr><td><strong>Type</strong></td><td>Default, Standalone, WithIcon</td><td>Default</td></tr>
              <tr><td><strong>Style</strong></td><td>Primary, Secondary, Subtle, Danger</td><td>Primary</td></tr>
              <tr><td><strong>State</strong></td><td>Default, Hover, Focus, Disabled</td><td>Default</td></tr>
              <tr><td><strong>Size</strong></td><td>Small, Medium, Large</td><td>Medium</td></tr>
              <tr><td><strong>Underline</strong></td><td>Always, HoverOnly, None</td><td>Always</td></tr>
              <tr><td><strong>RTL</strong></td><td>False, True</td><td>False</td></tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>

        <hr class="doc-divider" />

        <div class="doc-section">
          <h2 id="instance-overrides" class="doc-section-title">Instance Overrides</h2>
          <p class="doc-section-subtitle">Step-by-step guide for overriding TextLink instances in your design file.</p>
          <ul class="doc-list">
            <li><strong>Step 1:</strong> Select the TextLink instance on the canvas.</li>
            <li><strong>Step 2:</strong> In the properties panel, choose the desired <strong>Type</strong> (Default, Standalone, or WithIcon).</li>
            <li><strong>Step 3:</strong> Set the <strong>Style</strong> axis to match your semantic intent (Primary, Secondary, Subtle, or Danger).</li>
            <li><strong>Step 4:</strong> Configure the <strong>Underline</strong> mode based on context (Always for body text, HoverOnly for standalone).</li>
            <li><strong>Step 5:</strong> Toggle <strong>Show Leading Icon</strong> and <strong>Show Trailing Icon</strong> as needed.</li>
            <li><strong>Step 6:</strong> Override the <strong>Label</strong> text with your specific link copy.</li>
            <li><strong>Step 7:</strong> If targeting RTL users, set <strong>RTL = True</strong> to mirror the layout automatically.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- ======= ACCESSIBILITY TAB ======= -->
      <div class="tab-content" id="tab-accessibility" style="display: none; padding-top: 32px;">
        <h2 id="accessibility-overview" class="doc-section-title">Accessibility</h2>
        <p class="doc-section-subtitle">Guidelines for ensuring TextLink interactions are accessible across all assistive technologies.</p>

        <div class="doc-section">
          <h3 id="color-contrast" class="doc-h3">Color Contrast<span class="h3-badge" style="background: rgba(34,197,94,0.15); color: #16a34a;">WCAG AA Pass</span></h3>
          <p class="doc-section-subtitle">All TextLink styles must maintain sufficient contrast against their background according to WCAG 2.1.</p>
          <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 20px; margin-top: 24px;">
            <div style="background: var(--prism-surface); border: 1px solid var(--prism-border); border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden;">
              <div style="background: #fff; padding: 32px 24px; text-align: center;">
                <div style="font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; color: #2C66DD; text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 3px;">Primary Link</div>
              </div>
              <div style="padding: 16px 24px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; border-top: 1px solid var(--prism-border);">
                <div>
                  <div style="font-size: 13px; color: var(--prism-text-muted); font-weight: 600;">PRIMARY</div>
                  <div style="font-size: 15px; color: var(--prism-text); font-family: monospace; margin-top: 4px;">#2C66DD on #FFFFFF</div>
                </div>
                <div style="text-align: right;">
                  <div style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; background: rgba(34,197,94,0.1); color: #16a34a; padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 100px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700;">
                    <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg> 4.6:1
                  </div>
                  <div style="font-size: 11px; color: var(--prism-text-muted); margin-top: 4px; font-weight: 600;">WCAG AA Pass</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div style="background: var(--prism-surface); border: 1px solid var(--prism-border); border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden;">
              <div style="background: #fff; padding: 32px 24px; text-align: center;">
                <div style="font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; color: #C1181B; text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 3px;">Danger Link</div>
              </div>
              <div style="padding: 16px 24px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; border-top: 1px solid var(--prism-border);">
                <div>
                  <div style="font-size: 13px; color: var(--prism-text-muted); font-weight: 600;">DANGER</div>
                  <div style="font-size: 15px; color: var(--prism-text); font-family: monospace; margin-top: 4px;">#C1181B on #FFFFFF</div>
                </div>
                <div style="text-align: right;">
                  <div style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; background: rgba(34,197,94,0.1); color: #16a34a; padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 100px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700;">
                    <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg> 5.9:1
                  </div>
                  <div style="font-size: 11px; color: var(--prism-text-muted); margin-top: 4px; font-weight: 600;">WCAG AA Pass</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <hr class="doc-divider" />

        <div class="doc-section">
          <h3 id="keyboard-navigation" class="doc-h3">Keyboard Navigation</h3>
          <p class="doc-section-subtitle">Links must be fully operable via keyboard alone.</p>
          <table class="size-table">
            <thead><tr><th>Key</th><th>Action</th></tr></thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr><td><code>Tab</code></td><td>Move focus to the next focusable element.</td></tr>
              <tr><td><code>Shift + Tab</code></td><td>Move focus to the previous focusable element.</td></tr>
              <tr><td><code>Enter</code></td><td>Activate the focused link and navigate to its destination.</td></tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>

        <hr class="doc-divider" />

        <div class="doc-section">
          <h3 id="screen-reader" class="doc-h3">Screen Reader</h3>
          <p class="doc-section-subtitle">Ensure link purpose is communicated clearly to assistive technologies.</p>
          <ul class="doc-list">
            <li>Use the native <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">&lt;a&gt;</code> element with a valid <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">href</code> attribute to inherit default semantics.</li>
            <li>Link text must describe the destination. Avoid vague labels like "click here" or "read more".</li>
            <li>When icons are purely decorative, mark them with <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">aria-hidden="true"</code>.</li>
            <li>For external links, add <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">aria-label</code> or visually hidden text indicating "opens in a new tab".</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <hr class="doc-divider" />

        <div class="doc-section">
          <h3 id="disabled-state" class="doc-h3">Disabled State</h3>
          <p class="doc-section-subtitle">Disabled links require special handling since the <code>&lt;a&gt;</code> element has no native disabled attribute.</p>
          <ul class="doc-list">
            <li>Apply <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">aria-disabled="true"</code> and remove the <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">href</code> attribute or set it to <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">javascript:void(0)</code>.</li>
            <li>Set <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">tabindex="-1"</code> to remove the link from the tab order when disabled.</li>
            <li>Use <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">pointer-events: none</code> and <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">opacity: 0.5</code> for the visual disabled treatment.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <hr class="doc-divider" />

        <div class="doc-section">
          <h3 id="underline-a11y" class="doc-h3">Underline Accessibility</h3>
          <p class="doc-section-subtitle">Underline is a key accessibility signal for distinguishing links from surrounding text.</p>
          <ul class="doc-list">
            <li>Inside body text, <strong>always use Underline = Always</strong>. Color alone is insufficient to indicate a link per WCAG 1.4.1.</li>
            <li>If <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">Underline = None</code> is used, ensure the link is distinguishable by other visual means (e.g., icon, placement in a navigation context).</li>
            <li>The <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">text-underline-offset: 3px</code> token ensures the underline does not overlap descenders, improving legibility.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <hr class="doc-divider" />

        <div class="doc-section">
          <h3 id="rtl-a11y" class="doc-h3">RTL Accessibility</h3>
          <p class="doc-section-subtitle">Ensure RTL rendering preserves semantic meaning and reading order.</p>
          <ul class="doc-list">
            <li>Use the <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">dir="rtl"</code> attribute or CSS <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">direction: rtl</code> to mirror the link layout.</li>
            <li>Icon positions swap automatically. Ensure the logical order (leading/trailing) is preserved in the DOM.</li>
            <li>Screen readers follow DOM order regardless of visual direction, so keep the source order semantic.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      </div><!-- close main-content-inner -->

      <aside class="toc-sidebar">
        <h4 class="toc-heading">On this page</h4>
        <ul class="toc-nav" id="toc-nav">
